=== Months 2–6: Medium-Term Interventions

    / *$square.stroked$*: Pursue immunoadsorption if indicated (cognitive dysfunction + autoantibodies)
    / *$square.stroked$*: Trial low-dose IL-2 if Treg deficiency + autoimmune features
    / *$square.stroked$*: Trial estrogen if post-menopausal + low estradiol + high IL-6
    / *$square.stroked$*: If early disease ($<$3 years) + high cytokines → discuss anti-cytokine biologics
    / *$square.stroked$*: Continue all effective immediate protocols (pacing, MCAS, sleep, etc.)
    / *$square.stroked$*: Reassess every 4–6 weeks: What's working? What needs adjustment?

